{
    "name": "Ember Fox",
    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Ember Fox",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "Ember foxes resemble their canid namesakes, save for the flames that make their fur and the tips of their long whiskers flicker and glow. They particularly enjoy hunting elementals from the Plane of Wood.",
